974
01:27:34,920 --> 01:27:38,310
Now please bend your head as much as you can.

975
01:27:38,310 --> 01:27:45,530
Now remember to stretch back your fingers
so there is a good pressure on your scalp.

976
01:27:45,530 --> 01:27:48,380
Here again, I respect your freedom.

977
01:27:48,380 --> 01:27:51,800
I cannot force self-realization on you.

978
01:27:51,800 --> 01:28:00,800
So you have to say seven times, moving the
scalp seven times, you have to say: “Mother,

979
01:28:00,800 --> 01:28:03,390
please give me my self-realization.

980
01:28:03,390 --> 01:28:06,950
Mother, please give me my self-realization.”

981
