1003
01:30:38,750 --> 01:30:40,360
Forgive yourself and forgive others.

1004
01:30:40,360 --> 01:30:45,730
It will cool down, I’m sure it will cool
down.

1005
01:30:45,730 --> 01:30:52,330
Now once more only, please put your right
hand towards me and again put down the head

