01:30:52,330 --> 01:31:02,270
and with the left hand, please try to see
if there’s a cool or hot breeze like vibrations

1007
01:31:02,270 --> 01:31:05,770
coming out of your fontanelle bone area.

1008
01:31:05,770 --> 01:31:12,590
This is the actualization of baptism.

1009
01:31:12,590 --> 01:31:17,860
This is what is the Brahmarandhra Bheda that
