1010
01:31:17,860 --> 01:31:22,910
Now it’s done.

1011
01:31:22,910 --> 01:31:27,970
Don’t doubt.

1012
01:31:27,970 --> 01:31:36,090
Now please raise both the hands towards the
sky and push back your head and ask any one

1013
01:31:36,090 --> 01:31:39,200
